*To set up low hashrate notifications:

Levels:
Beginner - this feature is available by default.
Expert - To activate the feature, you need to accumulate a total of at least 30 Ph/s.
Ambassador - To activate the feature, you need to accumulate a total of at least 100 Ph/s.
